Achievements.Name: First Glory
Achievements.Description: Achieved with your first victory.

Achievements.Name: Winning Streak
Achievements.Description: Achieved after 10 straight wins.

Achievements.Name: Hat-trick Hunter
Achievements.Description: Achieved after scoring 5 hat-tricks.

Achievements.Name: Gentleman
Achievements.Description: Achieved when your foul per match ratio drops below 1 foul in the most recent 10 matches.

Achievements.Name: Owner
Achievements.Description: Achieved when your possession in the most recent 10 matches is above 60%.

Achievements.Name: Long Ranger
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you score from a distance of more than 35m.

Achievements.Name: World Traveller
Achievements.Description: Achieved when all stadiums have been used.

Achievements.Name: PK Master
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have won at least 10 penalty shootouts following regulation time.

Achievements.Name: Goal Getter
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have scored 100 goals.

Achievements.Name: Silver Service
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have made 100 assists.

Achievements.Name: 100 Matches
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have played 100 matches.

Achievements.Name: 100 Wins
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have won 100 matches.

Achievements.Name: Ace Striker
Achievements.Description: Achieved after 20 matches when you've scored an average of 2+ goals in the most recent 5 games.

Achievements.Name: Super Striker
Achievements.Description: Achieved after 100 matches when you've scored an average of 2.5+ goals in the most recent 10 games.

Achievements.Name: Attacking Midfielder
Achievements.Description: Achieved after 100 matches when your pass success ratio is 85% or more in the most recent 10 games.

Achievements.Name: Sniper
Achievements.Description: Achieved after 100 matches, when your shot success ratio is 70% or more in the most recent 10 games.

Achievements.Name: Brick Wall
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have kept 100 clean sheets.

Achievements.Name: England League Dominated
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have beaten all England League teams.

Achievements.Name: Ligue 1 Dominated
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have beaten all Ligue 1 teams.

Achievements.Name: Serie A Dominated
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have beaten all Serie A teams.

Achievements.Name: Eredivisie Dominated
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have beaten all Eredivisie teams.

Achievements.Name: Liga Española Dominated
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have beaten all Liga Española teams.

Achievements.Name: National Teams Dominated
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have beaten all national teams.

Achievements.Name: Ultimate Player
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have played 500 matches, scored 1000 goals and have won all leagues and cups.

Achievements.Name: Winning Streak (Xbox LIVE)
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you have 5 successive Ranked Match wins in the Xbox LIVE.

Achievements.Name: High Win Ratio
Achievements.Description: Achieved when your win ratio in Recent 20 match results of Xbox LIVE goes above 75%.

Achievements.Name: FK Goal
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you score from a free-kick directly in a Xbox LIVE Ranked Match.

Achievements.Name: Hat-trick Hunter (Xbox LIVE)
Achievements.Description: Achieved when you score a hat-trick in a Xbox LIVE Ranked Match.
